    metaTitle: "What Does Sofwave Feel Like? Real Experience Guide | Rani Beauty",
    metaDescription: "Curious about what Sofwave actually feels like? Walk through the entire treatment experience from arrival to aftercare with honest details about comfort and sensation.",
    excerpt: "Wondering what a Sofwave session actually feels like from start to finish? Here is an honest, detailed walkthrough of the entire treatment experience.",
    date: "April 29, 2026",
